lead_paragraph: Sunderland defender Billy Jones is hoping they can make the Stadium of Light a fortress after the basement side picked up their first Premier League home win of the season against fellow strugglers Hull City earlier this month.

headline.print_headline: Sunderland Must Make Stadium of Light a Fortress-Jones
